1b:T40a,Internal evidence clearly indicates this is a titanium intramedullary nail system for long bone fracture fixation. The CLAVO Ti brand system is evident from product_family and brochure_heading. Division (Trauma) and category (Intramedullary Nails) confirm implant class. Material (Titanium), locking capabilities (dynamic/static), and compression features are documented. However, no external verification available, no SKU examples, and brand field empty. The 'Ti' designation likely indicates titanium material variant within broader CLAVO family. Anatomy scope inferred from standard intramedullary nail applications (femur, tibia, humerus). Confidence reduced to 0.85 due to lack of external validation and missing brand confirmation. Recommend review to: (1) confirm CLAVO brand ownership/manufacturer relationship with Meril Life Sciences, (2) verify specific anatomical applications, (3) obtain product literature or catalog pages, (4) clarify if CLAVO Ti is distinct from other CLAVO variants (e.g., stainless steel versions).16:["$","$L1a",null,{"product":{"product_name":"CLAVO Ti Intramedullary Nail System","product_name_display":"Ti Intramedullary Nail System","sku_code":"MRL-CLV-001","product_family":"CLAVO Ti Intramedullary Nail System","product_family_display":"CLAVO Ti Intramedullary Nail System","slug":"clavo-ti-intramedullary-nail-system","images":[{"id":"92f0ceda32e1","storage_path":"agile-ortho/products/69c17bd504841ec9248cfabb/cover_6899289c.jpg","original_filename":"cover_Destiknee Brochure.pdf.jpg","content_type":"image/jpeg","size":208705,"uploaded_at":"2026-03-26T05:55:44.917719+00:00","source":"division_fallback","width":1600,"height":1600}],"status":"published","live_visible":true,"brochure_url":"agile-ortho/brochures/clavo-pfrn.pdf","seo_meta_title":"Ti Intramedullary Nail System | CLAVO Ti Intramedullary Nails - MedDevice Pro Telangana","seo_meta_description":"Meril's Nailing System is a professional-grade trauma implant system. Key features incl